import React from "react"; export default function Experience(){ return (<>

Software Developer, Avenir Health

November 2020 – August 2021

Avenir Health is an international health organization that projects outcomes of health interventions. During my time at Avenir I worked both in back-end and front-end software development for web and desktop applications including:

  • Coordinating with modelers, translating analytical health models into user-friendly applications.
  • Front-end website development using Javascript, React, HTML5, and CSS.
  • Back-end server development using Python.
  • Desktop application development using Delphi.

IT Support Technician, Webster Bank

June 2017 – October 2020

Answering help desk phone calls to remotely troubleshoot general company computer issues as well as password resets. Worked with applications such as SCCM, Active Directory, Citrix, RSA, and other proprietary banking applications.

Networking Technician, Central Connecticut State University

June 2015 – June 2017

Management of campus networking and telecom infrastructure. Configuration and management of campus switches, wire management, working in Cisco environments such as CUCM, Clean Access, NCS Prime, etc., Cisco VoIP phone support.

IT Onsite Support, Central Connecticut State University

August 2014 – June 2015

Providing technical support to clients around campus. Desktop support, virus removals, reimaging of workstations, SCCM management, Active Directory, Citrix, deployment of new computers, providing loaner machines, classroom support for media peripherals.

Geek Squad Advanced Repair Agent, Best Buy

April 2011 – August 2014
  • Work with clients on a daily basis troubleshooting computer issues.
  • Diagnostics of client machines as well as virus removals, general software issues.
  • Computer hardware installation
  • Cell phone screen replacement, troubleshooting, and activation
  • Manage daily reports and queues
